text: Helcion pectunculus, common name the prickly limpet, is a species of sea snail, a true limpet, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Patellidae, one of the families of true limpets. ==Description== ==Distribution== ==References== ==External links== * Category:Patellidae Category:Gastropods described in 1791
title: Helcion pectunculus
